#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "old animatronic fox"
msgid_plural "old animatronic foxes"
msgstr[0] "老舊電子動畫狐狸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'old animatronic fox', 'str_pl': 'old animatronic
#. foxes'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic fox, nearly twice your size.  Its teeth and claws look"
" quite sharp.  Its right hand is replaced with a hook.  It looks heavily "
"worn and degraded."
msgstr "一個雙足電子動畫狐狸，體型幾乎是你兩倍大。它的牙齒和爪子看起來相當鋒利。右手被一個鉤子取代。看起來嚴重磨損和退化。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "new animatronic fox"
msgid_plural "new animatronic foxes"
msgstr[0] "新型電子動畫狐狸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'new animatronic fox', 'str_pl': 'new animatronic
#. foxes'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic fox, nearly twice your size.  Its teeth and claws look"
" quite sharp.  Its outer layer is made of reinforced plastic.  It looks to "
"be high tech, and in good shape."
msgstr "一個雙足電子動畫狐狸，體型幾乎是你兩倍大。它的牙齒和爪子看起來相當鋒利。外層由強化塑料製成。看起來高科技且狀態良好。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "wrecked animatronic fox"
msgid_plural "wrecked animatronic foxes"
msgstr[0] "損毀的電子動畫狐狸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wrecked animatronic fox', 'str_pl': 'wrecked
#. animatronic foxes'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A wrecked animatronic fox, laying in a pile on the ground.  Its teeth and "
"claws still look quite sharp.  It's able to crawl around and climb on the "
"ceiling."
msgstr "一個損毀的電子動畫狐狸，癱在地上成一堆。它的牙齒和爪子仍然相當鋒利。能夠爬行並攀爬天花板。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "new animatronic bunny"
msgid_plural "new animatronic bunnies"
msgstr[0] "新型電子動畫兔子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'new animatronic bunny', 'str_pl': 'new
#. animatronic bunnies'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic bunny, nearly twice your size.  Its actually quite "
"cute, even though it's trying to kill you.  Its outer layer is made of "
"reinforced plastic.  It looks to be high tech, and in good shape."
msgstr "一個雙足電子動畫兔子，體型幾乎是你兩倍大。它實際上相當可愛，儘管它正試圖殺死你。外層由強化塑料製成。看起來高科技且狀態良好。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "old animatronic bunny"
msgid_plural "old animatronic bunnies"
msgstr[0] "老舊電子動畫兔子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'old animatronic bunny', 'str_pl': 'old
#. animatronic bunnies'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic bunny, nearly twice your size.  Its face has been torn"
" clear off, though the sockets for it's eyes still exist.  It looks heavily "
"worn and degraded."
msgstr "一個雙足電子動畫兔子，體型幾乎是你兩倍大。它的臉已被完全撕掉，不過眼睛的凹槽仍然存在。看起來嚴重磨損和退化。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "old animatronic chicken"
msgid_plural "old animatronic chickens"
msgstr[0] "老舊電子動畫雞"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'old animatronic chicken'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic chicken, nearly twice your size.  It's wearing a bib "
"that reads 'Let's Eat!'.  Though it is a robot, it stinks like death."
msgstr "一個雙足電子動畫雞，體型幾乎是你兩倍大。它戴著一條圍兜，上面寫著'開飯啦！'。儘管是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "new animatronic chicken"
msgid_plural "new animatronic chickens"
msgstr[0] "新型電子動畫雞"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'new animatronic chicken'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic chicken, nearly twice your size.  It's wearing a bib "
"that reads 'Let's Party!'.  She oddly has a curvaceous figure.  Its outer "
"layer is made of reinforced plastic.  It looks to be high tech, and in good "
"shape."
msgstr ""
"一個雙足電子動畫雞，體型幾乎是你兩倍大。它戴著一條圍兜，上面寫著'狂歡吧！'。奇怪的是，她有著曲線玲瓏的身材。外層由強化塑料製成。看起來高科技且狀態良好。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "old animatronic bear"
msgid_plural "old animatronic bears"
msgstr[0] "老舊電子動畫熊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'old animatronic bear'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic bear, nearly twice your size.  It's holding a "
"microphone, and wearing a top hat.  Though it is a robot, it stinks like "
"death.  It looks heavily worn and degraded."
msgstr "一個雙足電子動畫熊，體型幾乎是你兩倍大。它拿著麥克風，戴著高頂禮帽。儘管是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。看起來嚴重磨損和退化。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "new animatronic bear"
msgid_plural "new animatronic bears"
msgstr[0] "新型電子動畫熊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'new animatronic bear'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic bear, nearly twice your size.  It's holding a "
"microphone, and wearing a top hat.  Its outer layer is made of reinforced "
"plastic.  It looks to be high tech, and in good shape."
msgstr "一個雙足電子動畫熊，體型幾乎是你兩倍大。它拿著麥克風，戴著高頂禮帽。外層由強化塑料製成。看起來高科技且狀態良好。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic bat"
msgid_plural "animatronic bats"
msgstr[0] "電子動畫蝙蝠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic bat'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic bat, nearly twice your size.  It might have been cute "
"once, but has fallen into disrepair.  Though it is a robot, it stinks like "
"death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械蝙蝠，體型近乎你的兩倍。它或許曾很可愛，但現已破敗不堪。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic beaver"
msgid_plural "animatronic beavers"
msgstr[0] "機械海狸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic beaver'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic beaver, nearly twice your size.  Its buck teeth look "
"far more sharp than they should be.  Though it is a robot, it stinks like "
"death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械海狸，體型近乎你的兩倍。它的齙牙看起來異常鋒利。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic cat"
msgid_plural "animatronic cats"
msgstr[0] "機械貓"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic cat'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic cat, nearly twice your size.  Its claws are extremely "
"sharp.  Though it is a robot, it stinks like death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械貓，體型近乎你的兩倍。它的爪子極其銳利。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic chipmunk"
msgid_plural "animatronic chipmunks"
msgstr[0] "機械花栗鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic chipmunk'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic chipmunk, nearly twice your size.  You might call it "
"cute if it wasn't charging you down right now.  Though it is a robot, it "
"stinks like death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械花栗鼠，體型近乎你的兩倍。若非它正朝你衝來，你或許會覺得它可愛。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic cow"
msgid_plural "animatronic cows"
msgstr[0] "機械奶牛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic cow'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic cow, nearly twice your size.  Its voice-box is broken,"
" making it emit shrill, eerie moos.  Though it is a robot, it stinks like "
"death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械奶牛，體型近乎你的兩倍。它的發聲器已損壞，發出尖銳詭異的哞叫。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic coyote"
msgid_plural "animatronic coyotes"
msgstr[0] "機械郊狼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic coyote'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic coyote, nearly twice your size.  Its head twitches "
"about faster than seems possible.  Though it is a robot, it stinks like "
"death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械郊狼，體型近乎你的兩倍。它的頭部抽搐速度快得不可思議。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic deer"
msgid_plural "animatronic deers"
msgstr[0] "機械鹿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic deer'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic deer, nearly twice your size.  The hunter becomes the "
"hunted.  Though it is a robot, it stinks like death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械鹿，體型近乎你的兩倍。獵人與獵物的角色已然互換。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic horse"
msgid_plural "animatronic horses"
msgstr[0] "機械馬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic horse'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic horse, nearly twice your size.  It's amazing.  Though "
"it is a robot, it stinks like death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械馬，體型近乎你的兩倍。真是令人驚歎。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic pig"
msgid_plural "animatronic pigs"
msgstr[0] "機械豬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic pig'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic pig, nearly twice your size.  Little piggy go home, "
"little piggy no no.  Though it is a robot, it stinks like death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械豬，體型近乎你的兩倍。小豬回家去，小豬別別別。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic sheep"
msgid_plural "animatronic sheep"
msgstr[0] "機械綿羊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic sheep', 'str_pl': 'animatronic
#. sheep'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic sheep, nearly twice your size.  Its wool is mangy and "
"gross.  Though it is a robot, it stinks like death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械綿羊，體型近乎你的兩倍。它的羊毛髒亂不堪。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic squirrel"
msgid_plural "animatronic squirrels"
msgstr[0] "機械松鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic squirrel'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic squirrel, nearly twice your size.  Judging by its "
"sharp teeth, you hope it does not like nuts.  Though it is a robot, it "
"stinks like death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械松鼠，體型近乎你的兩倍。看它那鋒利的牙齒，你希望它不喜歡堅果。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic child"
msgid_plural "animatronic children"
msgstr[0] "機械兒童"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic child', 'str_pl': 'animatronic
#. children'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"An animatronic child.  It looks like it's annoying as hell.  Though it is a "
"robot, it stinks like death."
msgstr "一個機械兒童。它看起來煩人得要命。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "marionette"
msgid_plural "marionettes"
msgstr[0] "提線木偶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'marionette'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A marionette able to move itself around.  There are no strings on him "
"however."
msgstr "一個能自行移動的提線木偶。然而，它身上並沒有線。"

#: .\animatronics.json
msgid "animatronic wolf"
msgid_plural "animatronic wolves"
msgstr[0] "機械狼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'animatronic wolf', 'str_pl': 'animatronic
#. wolves'}
#: .\animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A bipedal animatronic wolf, nearly twice your size.  If the animal "
"counterpart was scary, this robot is terrifying.  Though it is a robot, it "
"stinks like death."
msgstr "一隻雙足機械狼，體型近乎你的兩倍。若說其動物原型已足夠駭人，這臺機器人則更加恐怖。雖是機器人，卻散發著死亡般的惡臭。"

#: .\bankrupt_pizzeria.json
msgid "Bankrupt Pizzeria"
msgstr "破產披薩店"

#: .\dead_animatronics.json
msgid "old broken animatronic fox"
msgid_plural "old broken animatronic foxes"
msgstr[0] "老舊破損的機械狐狸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'old broken animatronic fox', 'str_pl': 'old
#. broken animatronic foxes'}
#: .\dead_animatronics.json
msgid ""
"A broken animatronic fox.  If it was in bad shape before, it's a wreck now."
"  For some reason, it is oozing with blood - it's not your blood."
msgstr "一隻破損的機械狐狸。若說它之前狀況不佳，現在則已徹底報廢。不知為何，它正滲出鮮血——那不是你的血。"

