#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Animatronic Monsters"
msgstr "機械怪物"

#. ~ Description for Animatronic Monsters
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds a chain of bankrupt pizzerias, with still functioning animatronics "
"inside."
msgstr "添加了一系列破產的披薩店，裡面仍有運作的機械玩偶。"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is a crumpled old advertisement for a local pizzaria.  It depicts "
"smiling kids and some sort of animal mascot.  The flier reads \"Eat, rock, "
"party, play.\""
msgstr "這是一張皺巴巴的舊廣告，宣傳一家本地披薩店。上面畫著微笑的孩子們和某種動物吉祥物。傳單上寫著“吃、搖滾、派對、玩耍。”"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is a crumpled old advertisement for a local pizzaria.  It depicts "
"smiling kids and some sort of animal mascot.  The flier reads \"Eat, rock, "
"party, play!\"  Someone has crudely scrawled underneath it \"Smoke weed "
"every day!\""
msgstr ""
"這是一張皺巴巴的舊廣告，宣傳一家本地披薩店。上面畫著微笑的孩子們和某種動物吉祥物。傳單上寫著“吃、搖滾、派對、玩耍！”有人在下面潦草地塗鴉著“每天抽大麻！”"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"This is a kids place, why is their mascot so stacked!?\""
msgstr "“這是個兒童場所，為什麼他們的吉祥物身材這麼火辣！？”"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"NO BAD ROBOT I DON'T WANT PIZZA.\""
msgstr "“不，壞機器人，我不要披薩。”"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"Fuckin haunted pizza joint, just burn it down\""
msgstr "“該死的鬧鬼披薩店，乾脆燒了它”"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"Pizza, arcade tokens, horrible death, got my bases covered.\""
msgstr "“披薩、街機代幣、可怕的死亡，我的基本需求都齊了。”"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"leg eaten by zombie robot furry help\""
msgstr "“腿被殭屍機器人獸迷吃了 救命”"

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Don't make me have ye walk the plank.\""
msgstr "“別逼我讓你走跳板。”"

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Welcome to the pirate's cove matey!\""
msgstr "“歡迎來到海盜灣，夥計！”"

#: .\speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Arr, ahoy there maties!  And welcom- welcom- welcome to tha pirate's "
"cove.\""
msgstr "“啊嗬，喂，夥計們！歡迎——歡迎——歡迎來到海盜灣。”"

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"It's me.\""
msgstr "“是我。”"

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"SKREEEEEEEEEEEEEE!\""
msgstr "“嘶啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！”"

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Dum de dum dum dum.\""
msgstr "“咚嘚咚咚咚。”"

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Ahoy there!\""
msgstr "“啊嗬，你好！”"

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"They will know the joy of creation.\""
msgstr "“他們將知曉創造的喜悅。”"

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Ha huhuhu huh huh.\""
msgstr "\"哈呼呼呼呼哈呼。\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Let's eat!\""
msgstr "\"開飯啦！\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Hello!\""
msgstr "\"你好！\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Hai!\""
msgstr "\"嗨！\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Hi!\""
msgstr "\"嗨！\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Let's play!\""
msgstr "\"一起玩吧！\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"What's your name little child?\""
msgstr "\"小朋友，你叫什麼名字？\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Come closer.\""
msgstr "\"靠近點。\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Come play with me!\""
msgstr "\"來和我一起玩吧！\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"No running.\""
msgstr "\"禁止奔跑。\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Running is against the rules.\""
msgstr "\"奔跑是違反規定的。\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"RAAAAGGGGRRRHHH!\""
